        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> while I'd almost agree that something is weird with dr/pr spells, I'd hardly suggset that ebolt and coc are useless, as you state they may be.</P><P>Their resist rate on normal xp mobs is no better or worse than any other spells we might use, excepting lifetaps.</P><P>Our debuff line really needs fixed, the mana cost for those spells is disproportionatley high, and the resist rate is through the freakin' roof. It's cheaper to cast a dot twice than debuff and dot seperatley.</P><P>High agro from dr/pr spells is just a part of the game I think.</P><P><a href="http://xzzy.org/ereet/" target="_blank">http://xzzy.org/ereet/</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
