        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> I dont know if theyre bugged. My theory about counters was always that the spell is applied that often(aggro) with doing a resistance check every time(resists). Also I have to admit that there seems something bugged because I could easily cast CE on velketor 3 times without resists but last time after the patch didnt get one through.<BR>So there might be some hidden code which inceases the resistcheck every counter or on the 2nd+ counter resist debuffs dont matter at all(bug).</P><P>Thats why I usually name(d) dots witout counters "lure dots" ;)</P><P></P><P>Sage Nelle Sukkubus of Wolfsclan, SolRo</P><P><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=77291" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=77291</a><BR>-- <BR>255 chars are not enough for a signature!<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
